speaking-unknown-id.title: Ms.
speaking-unknown-id.name: SCHULTZ, WASSERMAN
speaking-unknown-id.paragraph: Mr. Speaker, I move that the House do now adjourn.
The motion was agreed to; accordingly (at 4 o'clock and 5 minutes p.m.), under its previous order, the House adjourned until Monday, June 11, 2007, at 12:30 p.m., for morning-hour debate.
